<plot>Oil Tribe is a short documentary, that follows three characters. Jeff is a small business owner being affected by high fuel costs. Jen and Norm are both university professors that explain why fuel cost are so high. They express interesting views about high gas prices. The film triggers your thinking about fuel costs, and how the prices have affected everyone.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?408883</url></doc>
